title: Predators stay unbeaten with 3-1 win over Devils
text: Predators stay unbeaten with 3-1 win over Devils OCT 13, 10:35 pm The Predators are off to a 3-0 start to the 2015-16 season. Roman Jose weighs in on the team's 3-1 win over the Devils on Tuesday night.
